high_descs: Turn around, then move forward a bit, then turn right and head to the sink.
Pick up the pink bar of soap from the sink.
Turn left and move forward to the wall, then turn right and face the left sink.
Put the bar of soap into the sink, then fill the sink with water, then take the bar of soap out of the sink.
Turn around, move forward a bit, then turn around and face the white cabinet below the sink.
Open the left door of the white cabinet and put the bar of soap inside, then close the door to the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet bar of soap into the white cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around, take a step forward, and then turn right towards the bar soap on the counter.
Pick up the soap from the counter.
Turn left and go to the sink next to the wall.
Place the soap in the sink, wash it, and pick it back up.
Take a step backwards to find the cabinet below the sink beside the wall.
Place the soap in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Wash the soap on the counter in addition to placing it in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around, then go to the first sink to your right.
Pick up the bar of soap from the counter on the right of the sink.
Take the soap to the left sink.
Wash the bar of soap in the left side sink.
Look down to the cabinet sunder the sink.
Put the bar of soap in the right front corner of the far left cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap into an under-sink cabinet.
